{"root":{"data":{"id":"djin8axefug0","created":1782442775759,"text":"测铜绿微囊藻昼夜 pH 曲线"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djin8unq1ww0","created":1782442818709,"text":"铜绿微囊藻正常培养\n\t           ↓\n12 h 光 / 12 h 暗\n\t           ↓\n用 pH 计每 2–4 h 测一次 bulk pH\n\t           ↓\n连续测 2–3 个昼夜周期\n\t           ↓\n得到真实 pH 曲线","font-family":"times new roman","font-size":16},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djinanq0zxs0","created":1782442960340,"text":"基于实测 pH 曲线制备 pH-PBAT","layout_mind_offset":{"x":243.99999636411667,"y":251.99999624490744}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djinbiooejc0","created":1782443027738,"text":"Raw-PBAT fragments\n\t            ↓\n加入无藻培养基或模拟培养基\n\t            ↓\n暗期条件：调到低 pH，例如 7.4，维持 12 h\n\t            ↓\n光期条件：调到高 pH，例如 9.2，维持 12 h\n\t           ↓\n重复 3、7、14 个周期\n\t           ↓\n分离固体和水相","layout_left_offset":{"x":-226.99999661743647,"y":-12.999999806284904}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djinci6ri4w0","created":1782443105019,"text":"pH-PBAT-solid"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djincjfo4ww0","created":1782443107734,"text":"pH-PBAT-leachate"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}